testsuite.name: oradb::is_oracle_patch_installed with invalid parameters with wrong number of parameters

testcase.name: oradb::is_oracle_patch_installed with invalid parameters with wrong number of parameters should run oradb::is_oracle_patch_installed() and raise an ArgumentError with the message matching /expects 2 arguments/

oradb::is_oracle_patch_installed with invalid parameters with wrong number of parameters should run oradb::is_oracle_patch_installed("/u01/app/oracle/product/12.1.0/dbhome_1") and raise an ArgumentError with the message matching /expects 2 arguments/
